text: Michel Nakouzi (born 5 May 1932) is a Lebanese wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Lebanese male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Lebanon Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Beirut
